{"tid":1775500,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"又話大三罷，人呢？","createTime":"2019-12-09T01:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T12:51:25.000Z","uid":224656,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a05abf1e81ff698ab4358bd885ddbdfbe07fdc8c","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"係咪我又比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，每次吹雞話大三罷我都唔怕比人炒出離，一次失望過一次，真係好灰機<br />\n<br />\n琴日遊行個個大叫129大三罷，工會我又報左名（工會仲等緊審批），黎明行動文宣今次都好足丫？結果今朝6點企條街度等，一直都無乜人，到8點d人話散水，搞左咁耐宣傳都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人屌唔罷工既人，無錯係要屌，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但大三罷唔止罷工，仲有罷課同罷市！</span><br />\n大家記唔記得？你今朝唔出離，都希望你參與罷市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後跪求大家，你罷左工無出黎明行動又好，返左公司扮工又好，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊出離和你lunch好無呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多你一個真係好撚多呀，場仗未打完架！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b272d97ad6920a7034f0e9f47093e336d6a972a","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"又話128死線129搞大佢，大家記唔記得死線？<br />\n唔好琴日出離行下當玩就算，今朝繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工會手足可唔可以幫幫手落力催谷，睇住d工會谷同三罷谷不停有人入，係好多人，但無人提今日行動，連三罷谷都好少人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff37712cd313a7990ec6bec66691586333fadfb8","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1f274aabd7565294eb94d17bd6cce692564bc825","tid":1775500,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:55:25.000Z","msg":"講個笑話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月9日黎明行動，大3罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ccf48403d5b034b8c05a99a0530b46b0e4b370","tid":1775500,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"完全係狼來了戰術 老實罷一兩日同打個風冇分別<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">白領工會 招募會員</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z0UyNk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z0UyNk.jpg&h=c1d779b0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n會員入會表格👇<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/FB5547eGgNqT34ma8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FFB5547eGgNqT34ma8&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=c8b1f8e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/FB5547eGgNqT34ma8</a><br />\n12.13 1300-1500 尖沙咀街站<br />\n12.14 1200-1400 觀塘.荔枝角街站<br />\n12.20 1300-1500 中環街站"},{"pid":"a13d3af97fe192fe353133799acb57d88ee723ee","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48ccf48403d5b034b8c05a99a0530b46b0e4b370","tid":1775500,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"完全係狼來了戰術 老實罷一兩日同打個風冇分別<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">白領工會 招募會員</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z0UyNk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z0UyNk.jpg&h=c1d779b0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><