cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"罷咗咁多次冇效會越黎越少人係人之常情<br />\n越冇人 越有機會比人拉<br />\n越有機會比人拉 越少人<br />\n同埋依家沒有大事發生 冇推動力去一兩日搞罷工<br />\n依家係要轉型為長遠抗爭啦<br />\n宜搞集會遊行同放映會 繼續連結大家既理念<br />\n街頭勇武少之有少 開花就更難"},{"pid":"617eabb5b8d5c93c55b7e103f61209ec80951778","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"班狗就嚴陣以待出哂去，我地就乜人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e42089a56e79c790407fa0de21a00da1266b458","tid":1775500,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"617eabb5b8d5c93c55b7e103f61209ec80951778","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"班狗就嚴陣以待出哂去，我地就乜人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"你都識講對家嚴陣以待，仲要主動過去比人拉？<br />\n<br />\n一齊做多d宣傳街站，搞工會令多d人加入好過啦<br />\n人地法國罷工背後都搞左好耐架<br />\n我地真係話搞工會搞得個一個月左右炸"},{"pid":"53a8662a4be8a95d1c01e339acb8afe1af7524f0","tid":1775500,"uid":224656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"84ccf662f0ad224e523cd0d1f12bdfdb701355d3","tid":1775500,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"老點你又真係去, 攪手仲未起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862c4a2d569552abd4600515a99fdd765f79e710","tid":1775500,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"對唔住🙇🏻&zwj;♂️，借個位宣傳一下：<br />\n<br />\n和你開工會：七人成團，重光勞工界，只剩唔夠四個月！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"510d454675a2cf415f0efb16e82059a06c66db28","tid":1775500,